{"tid":938184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"痴L線！當呢度係大陸？！【中港車剷安全島U-turn】","createTime":"2018-12-12T06:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T06:42:03.000Z","uid":225464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e12c116334c64e3ce66d470d71b4bca30a76a161","tid":938184,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181212%2Fbkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html&d=O5JMslzyeRwB2U9kY%2FOhhwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4f08d78a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212131206800-1212_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Li2o11t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLi2o11t.jpg&h=1acb6a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>中港車打橫行　剷安全島掉頭　途人嚇到呆</strong><br />\n行人即使跟足交通燈號過路，都要打醒精神注意路況，因為隨時遇到亂來的司機。近日灣仔有中港車為求掉頭，就上演了一幕「大地任我行」。<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「香港交通突發報料區」的片段可見，星期一（10日）下午4時許，一輛中港車在灣仔軒尼詩道近史釗域道燈位的路旁轉出，打橫連切兩線，駛到右線「埋定靚位」。<br />\n<br />\n當行車燈號由綠轉黃，中港車即駛出行人過路處，右轉上安全島掉頭。當時安全島尚有途人正等待過路，顯得十分吃驚，有女士立即拉開孩子避過車輛。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者表示，事後已到附近警署報案，並引述警員當時的話︰「夠晒料，交通部見啦」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評中港車為馬路炸彈，怒斥：「好離譜」、「呢啲肯定係明知故犯」、「咁誇張&hellip;仲要有人等緊過馬路」、「佢以為自己喺大陸揸緊車，罔顧生死」。"},{"pid":"dc6e2df2ccdcc808d7deb8ac215fd4830db6f3a0","tid":938184,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"係時侯移民"},{"pid":"3d2aff785323a36e2336aaba1aaf9e8b6ed51b00","tid":938184,"uid":63909,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"大陸車牌<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"6881c0d3f583a5193cc2a6318031247f8b79ed6d","tid":938184,"uid":79410,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲告得危駕"},{"pid":"e1450c42812442e808d92f13b8813c0b106f2c4a","tid":938184,"uid":68746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀見過中港車十字燈位綠燈照轉左，以為自己喺大陸揸車？"},{"pid":"79f6ac5c531a9993ae1eb31d0d5bb34e9231075f","tid":938184,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸人真是無守法意識"},{"pid":"4805a9420a67f323340d6bf34072cdce68001d16","tid":938184,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"仲洗打格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e04edebb7624b136022e28cf7400645fdb8298","tid":938184,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔出奇啦 琴晚先比架左呔連cut2線閘埋黎<br />\n差啲炒車"},{"pid":"7ab7a73a85d5c8eb8d099819f11b059409c45142","tid":938184,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1450c42812442e808d92f13b8813c0b106f2c4a","tid":938184,"uid":68746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀見過中港車十字燈位綠燈照轉左，以為自己喺大陸揸車？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"支港私家車不嬲都無品亂行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79737db48c5b38896c9084df7e2fc3b2e4b98748","tid":938184,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667881701251c522d8fa8b3b3d18370cd8f4551f","tid":938184,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"迴旋處逆線都係咁<br />\n你放得支那車入黎就遇左"},{"pid":"12daa443d8bc3ea6fbf4b61a57759bff26123ecd","tid":938184,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"香港車，有大陸牌"},{"pid":"e5b2a75e026b7700d08b67eaca9fd21f5325d8ab","tid":938184,"uid":14737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1450c4